title: - broad city web series -
description:
Broad City - The Complete Web Series

This is the actual show they created for the web before it got picked up by comedy central. i renamed them all and pulled metadata info so it can be loaded in xbmc/kodi or some other media players. Everything is in order except the bloopers which are in their own folder.

All files should be in mp4 format, mostly in 720p, but some of the earlier episodes in lower resolution.

Enjoy and share!
